flowchart TD

Start([API Request Received])

Start --> ParseRequest[Parse Request<br>question + domain]

ParseRequest --> LoadDomain[Load Domain Config]

LoadDomain --> LoadCatalog[Load Dataset Catalog]

LoadCatalog --> BuildContext[Build Prompt Context]

BuildContext --> SemanticRetrieval[Semantic Retrieval<br>Vector Search]

SemanticRetrieval --> CallPlanner[Call LLM Planner]

CallPlanner --> QuerySpec[Generate QuerySpec]

QuerySpec --> ValidateSpec{QuerySpec Valid?}

ValidateSpec -->|No| Clarify[Return Clarification]

ValidateSpec -->|Yes| CostGuard[Query Cost Guardrail]

CostGuard --> ResolveDataset[Dataset Resolver]

ResolveDataset --> BuildSQL[SQL Builder]

BuildSQL --> CacheCheck{Cache Hit?}

CacheCheck -->|Yes| LoadCache[Return Cached Result]

CacheCheck -->|No| ExecuteSQL[Execute SQL Query]

ExecuteSQL --> StoreCache[Store Result in Cache]

StoreCache --> FormatResult[Format Response]

LoadCache --> FormatResult

FormatResult --> UpdateSession[Update Session Memory]

UpdateSession --> ReturnResponse([Return Response to User])
